summary: Why did you choose long live and sweeter than fiction tattoos?
question: Why did you choose long live and sweeter than fiction tattoos?
answer:
I’d been thinking about what Taylor tattoo I would get for years and for a while it was Fearless but I decided on Long Live because it really encompasses the spirit and energy and feeling of the experiences I’ve had because of and with Taylor. 

Sweeter Than Fiction was something I kept singing in Melbourne when we were there for the Rep tour and the entire song is so uplifting and motivating and it really just makes me feel so good. Also I’m a writer so it’s very fitting. 

send me anything and i’ll reply with gifs
